# Mean of all available history

mean_forecast <- meanf(UKgas,9)
plot(mean_forecast)

mean_forecast <- meanf(UKgas,12)
plot(mean_forecast)

# Naive Model
naive_forecast <- naive(UKgas,4)
plot(naive_forecast)

naive_forecast <- naive(UKgas,5)
plot(naive_forecast)

naive_forecast <- naive(UKgas,8)
plot(naive_forecast)

# Random Walk
rwf_forecast <- rwf(UKgas,8)
rwf_forecast <- rwf(UKgas,8, drift=TRUE)
# Seasonal Naive Model
snaive_forecast <- snaive(UKgas,8)

# Moving Averages

MA5_forecast <- ma(UKgas,order=5)
MA9_forecast <- ma(UKgas,order=9)

# Collation of all the above
plot(mean_forecast)
lines(naive_forecast$mean,col="red")
lines(rwf_forecast$mean,col="green")
lines(snaive_forecast$mean,col="black")
lines(MA5_forecast,col="Pink")
lines(MA9_forecast,col="Blue")
